==English==
===Etymology===
: [[free]] + [[recycle]]

===Noun===
'''Freecycle(tm)'''
# (US) The trademarked name of the Worldwide Organization (The Freecycle Network) where people can freely give items to other people. Started in Tucson, Arizona by Deron Beal, it has spread around the world. Many people have joined the Freecycle Network and some have since left in order to start their own variations of the Freecycle Network.

